headline.print_headline: Mars 'Flying Saucer' Splashes Down After NASA Test
headline.main: Mars 'Flying Saucer' Splashes Down After NASA Test

lead_paragraph: A saucer-shaped NASA vehicle testing new technology for Mars landings rocketed high over the Pacific on Saturday and deployed a novel inflatable braking system, but its massive parachute failed to fully unfurl as it descended to a splashdown.
